{"tid":1560141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際戰線] 全球齊篤灰2.0 向WhatsApp篤灰 #wtsappforhk #standwithhk","createTime":"2019-09-11T05:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T17:33:41.000Z","uid":91558,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"25e187f93b1c1fdfe70f5c21e20ad50ad5cbb286","tid":1560141,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"眼見黑警咁明目張膽咁開展文革2.0，我地都要努力開拓新戰線<br />\n順便煲大警暴同白色恐怖<br />\nWhatsApp喺外國都多人用，一於拉埋外國勢力落水！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日po過一次，已有巴絲喺twitter推hashtag<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請即參與：#wtsappforhk campaign (#eye4hk 2.0)</span></span></strong><br />\n有twitter既快啲retweet，無twitter既而家開番個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">本地線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n1. 將警暴，藍絲，官員，議員罪證狂推比警察<br />\n2. 為左令每一個負責mon住既阿sir都不愁寂莫，每個人睇番自己生日日子既最後一位數字，揀下表有同樣最尾位數字既電話<br />\n3. 有關如何保護自己，請搜尋「太空」等相關字眼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n1. retweet手足既呢條tweet, 記住comment加#wtsappforhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=37d6b641\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&h=44f2ff93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21</a><br />\n2. 如果你選擇將10個電話重新打一次出黎，記得加+852<br />\n3. 叫埋外國人一齊Report俾WhatsApp聽，增加noise<br />\n尾數雙數先係business<br />\n單數係正常account<br />\n大家report要認真少少！<br />\n班狗想分散投資，不過我地要port到佢一條不留！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正常帳戶 Terms</span>: <a href=\"https://www.whatsapp.com/legal/#terms-of-service\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Flegal%2F%23terms-of-service&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=bc65bddc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.whatsapp.com/legal/#terms-of-service</a><br />\nAcceptable use of our service: <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(f) involve any non-personal use of our Services unless otherwise authorized by us.</span></strong><br />\nReport email: support@whatsapp.com<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">商業帳戶 Terms</span>: <a href=\"https://www.whatsapp.com/legal/business-terms/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Flegal%2Fbusiness-terms%2F&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWXqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=33811a1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.whatsapp.com/legal/business-terms/</a><br />\nCompany must not directly, indirectly, or through automated or other means:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(b) engage in any harassing, threatening, intimidating, predatory, or stalking conduct; <br />\n(e) collect information of or about other users in any impermissible or unauthorized manner; <br />\n(f) use our Business Services other than for their intended purpose or interfere with, disrupt, negatively affect, or inhibit other users; </span></strong><br />\nReport email: smb_web@support.whatsapp.com<br />\n得閒add哂d狗電話，逐個再禁出黎舉報多一次啦<br />\n祝大家舉報愉快<br />\n<br />\n好處： <br />\n成本低，可以迫大家儲下唔同角度文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n壞處：<br />\n外國人參與國際線程度成疑，但以campaign之名，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行宣傳之實</span></span></strong>。就咁講#chinazi，#culturalrevolution，人地未必咁get，叫埋佢地一齊行動就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整左兩張圖希望大家就內容同排版俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次寫行動po 請屌細力啲<img src=\"/a